videos.description: Terry Swanson bounces to the outside and takes it to the house for a 48-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Toledo scores TD on 4th down

videos.description: Terry Swanson finds the end zone again, this time for a 22-yard touchdown run to give Toledo a 17-0 lead.
videos.headline: Swanson scores second TD

videos.description: DeDarallo Blue bounces off a tackle for a 39- yard run to put Toledo inside the 10.
videos.headline: Blue breaks a tackle to put Toledo in the red zone

videos.description: Logan Woodside keeps it for a 5-yard touchdown run to put Toledo up 23-3.
videos.headline: Woodside scores TD on QB keeper

videos.description: Justin Clark picks off Shane Morris' pass at Toledo's 46-yard line.
videos.headline: Toledo forces Central Michigan turnover

videos.description: Shakif Seymour scores his first touchdown of the game with an 8-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Seymour punches in another Toledo TD
